<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="prose">
      <p><strong>There is so much we can learn from each other</strong></p>

      <div class="two-col-img">
        <img src="/images/elementor/thumbs/about1-video-overlay-r1y4ib5o6zkk0do531e69gikcuh3kb9qgd7o36t0a0.jpg" alt="Healthcare professionals sharing knowledge in a video discussion">
